info.name: IS_X509CERTIFICATE_CONTAINS_TSLSIGNING_EXT_KEY_USAGE
info.description: ExtendedKeyUsage extension should be present containing id-tsl-kp-tslSigning.

info.name: IS_X509CERTIFICATE_CONTAINS_SUBJECT_KEY_IDENTIFIER
info.description: SubjectKeyIdentifier extension shall be present using one of the first 2 methods specified in clause 4.2.1.2 of RFC 5280.
